A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Reverend Corey J. Neal on the occasion of his 17th pastoral
2 anniversary; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Reverend Corey J. Neal answered the call to ministry at the age of 27 after a
4 transformative series of hardships led him to relinquish his personal plans and embrace God's
5 purpose, committing himself to preaching and serving in Columbus, Georgia; and
6 WHEREAS, Reverend Corey J. Neal was called by the Lord 17 years ago to lead the
7 congregation of Greater Peace Baptist Church; and
8 WHEREAS, prior to becoming the church's senior pastor, he faithfully served as director of
9 Christian education, youth pastor, and assistant pastor under the leadership of his
10 grandfather, Reverend E. L. Sullivan; and
11 WHEREAS, during his distinguished tenure, Reverend Corey J. Neal has established
12 numerous programs and workshops, including those focused on health, finances, and
13 employment, that have improved the spiritual growth and well-being of the church and the
14 surrounding community; and
